Package: findPC
Type: Package
Title: Automatically select number of principal components in single-cell analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Haotian Zhuang, Zhicheng Ji
Maintainer: Haotian Zhuang <haotian.zhuang@duke.edu>
Description: findPC is a software tool including six methods to automatically determine the optimal number of principal components to retain based on the standard deviations explained by each PC. 
    A major advantage of findPC is that the only information required is a series of standard deviations explained by each PC.
License: 
Imports: ggplot2, grid, gridExtra, reshape2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
